sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant JobSetCtrl as JobSet Controller
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (rank 0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl create TrainJob<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS (auto-rotated)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
        K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainJob, TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime spec resolved
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE/PATCH JobSet<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy (RHAI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: UPDATE TrainJob/status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

        K8sAPI->>JobSetCtrl: Watch event: JobSet created
        JobSetCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Jobs/Pods
        K8sAPI-->>TrainingPod: Pods scheduled and started
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking
        Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (for TrainJob)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (find rank 0 pod IP)
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy restricted)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training metrics (loss, epoch, step)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
        Note over Controller,TrainingPod: Flow 3: MPI Distributed Training Setup
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret (SSH RSA key pair)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE ConfigMap (MPI hostfile)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

        Note over TrainingPod: MPI Launcher Pod
        TrainingPod->>TrainingPod: SSH to worker pods<br/>2222/TCP SSH<br/>Auth: RSA key pair
    end
